# Docker Compose debugging: check implementation + file selection first

When there are Docker Compose errors (especially confusing parse/interpolation errors), do **not** start by changing YAML. First confirm **which Compose implementation** and **which compose file** are actually in play.

## Rule (guardrail)

- Do not start by changing YAML. First confirm Compose implementation + compose file selection.

